How do you install the RegKey?

Everyone that is having problems installing the regkey, I figured out how to do so. All the directions can be found within the serial.txt file within the Cool Edit Pro rar you downloaded. Here is what to do!! 1. Create a new folder name Cool Edit Pro 2.0, then unzip the file you downloaded inside that folder. After you download and unzip the file, 2. Install the cepstup.exe found in folder CEP 2.0. Run Cep2reg.exe and when prompted insert the following name and key as follows:

User: Marco Hardmeier 
Pass: 200-00-Z3738EJ5

3. Now install cepsetup.exe found insider folder CEP 2.1 and you will upgrade Cool Edit Pro from version 2.0 to version 2.1

Also this program does wonders with Fl Studio 10 XXl producer Edition. Best digital combo for making beats! Been using both since 1999, when there was just  Cool Edit Pro, and Fruity Loops "Fl Studio 1" was the name then!
